data.description:
*HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS*
Welcome to this stunning, almost brand-new gem built in 2022, nestled in the highly sought-after Rivertown community. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the elegance of crown molding gracing the main living spaces. The heart of the home boasts a spacious kitchen with a generous island, perfect for entertaining and family gatherings. A separate oven and gas cooktop ensure that cooking for loved ones is a breeze. The walk-in pantry adds to the convenience of this culinary haven. Ceiling fans are thoughtfully installed throughout the home, ensuring a comfortable and cool environment year-round. Step through the sliding doors, and you'll find a screened-in porch that overlooks a tranquil pond - the ideal spot for sipping your morning coffee or unwinding in the evening. The fully fenced backyard is perfect for your furry friends to play and explore. The owner's suite is a true retreat, featuring large walk-in closets and a picture-perfect view of the pond. The owner's bathroom suite offers dual vanities for added luxury. Even the garage isn't overlooked, with its sleek grey epoxy floor. Living in Rivertown means you'll have access to a plethora of amenities. Multiple pools, full gyms, tennis courts, baseball fields, soccer fields, running and bike trails, and even a media room - the list goes on and on, ensuring that there's always something fun to do right within your community. This property is a perfect combination of modern comfort and a vibrant, active community lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your new home sweet home!
